{"tid":985602,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"警司應該食得好和味！","createTime":"2019-01-17T17:41:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T01:57:17.000Z","uid":34773,"like":107,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"99367ce88d12d2194cae500add72d70602cfcfb0","tid":985602,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T17:41:10.000Z","msg":"你班連登仔極膚淺唔食識，警司應該食得好爽。<br />\n諗下張條肉龍放入一個<br />\n有權力<br />\n有勢力<br />\n有學識<br />\n虔誠耶教徒<br />\n老公有地位既人妻體內，<br />\n<br />\n仲要係香港警隊最自豪安全既屋入面，<br />\n面向倒掛十字架，聖母像，<br />\n唸住性母經悔改地日夜抽插，<br />\n射晒d 熱白濃精入去蜜洞。<br />\n<br />\n每一晚偷情都好似去左<br />\n耶穌出身地耶路殺冷隱世草叢，<br />\nor ifc 天台渣住支搶同朝偉對視壓力場面，<br />\n個種刺激感，至高無上既安全感，超逾上帝既感覺你地唔會明。<br />\n<br />\n心癮起上黎就算個人妻係catgirl 咁款，都可以奶到雪雪聲，連美極都唔洗落！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你班傻尻仲係度天滅中共，平反64<br />\n人地警司放低左輪拎起第二支搶出黎劣緊。"},{"pid":"8ae0635966c3aa6512ab7c90f00dacff86a19de6","tid":985602,"uid":34773,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T00:18:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fadf27ec86ea702484cc9ae757d905e45df377fe","tid":985602,"uid":40779,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T00:22:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07c5c86dc1ee04ed600c1a1d1fc9462486caf29c","tid":985602,"uid":126219,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T00:28:20.000Z","msg":"認同，個黑警好明顯唔係食相頭<br />\n係食個意境"},{"pid":"7f69b1cca1e0e916defcce23403bb6db9ecff57f","tid":985602,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T00:30:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8dafd8fc33112f6dd878bbebca87bb70b9a4a83","tid":985602,"uid":130901,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T00:37:52.000Z","msg":"就好似楊受成玩某D樣衰女星一樣，大班人朝拜既偶像含緊條撚，再